original_title: Smith Rock 1986: The Birth of U.S. Sport Climbing
overview: The lycra was scary and sport climbing was being discovered in the U.S. Featuring Alan Watts, J.B. Tribout, Todd Skinner, Beth Wald and many others. This historic DVD features both traditional rock climbing and sport climbing at Smith Rock in Central Oregon.
title: Smith Rock 1986: The Birth of U.S. Sport Climbing
